This breathtaking castle located in Jupiter, FL,  includes custom designed and hand-painted murals on all ceilings, as well as polished marble and wood flooring throughout. The kitchen, designed for the gourmet chef, provides a well-designed workspace. The spacious dining room can accommodate 14 guests and includes custom, built in storage cabinets. The bar and wine room features copious amounts of storage for glassware, as well as 245 bottles of wine with a dedicated cooling system. For more information, email us at info@piquetrealty.com.

A cozinha, projetada para o chef gourmet, oferece um brilhante espaço de trabalho. Já a espaçosa sala de jantar - acomoda 14 pessoas - e ainda inclui armários customizados. O local apresenta também um espaço capaz de armazenar cerca de 245 garrafas de vinho, com um sofisticado sistema de refrigeração. Para mais informações, envie um e-mail para info@piquetrealty.com.
